POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (56): GLOBAL (PAPUA NEW GUINEA, DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF THE CONGO, NIGERIA) CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUSES, CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 2 POST ORAL POLIOVIRUS VACCINE TYPE 2 CESSATION
