[There have been 6 newly confirmed cases of cVDPV reported by 3 countries during the last week, with 2 of the 3 endemic countries reporting positive environmental samples with WPV1 isolated. Impression: wild polioviruses continue to circulate in 2 of the 3 endemic countries (Pakistan and Afghanistan), and circulating vaccine derived polioviruses continue to circulate in 5 countries (Nigeria, DR Congo, Papua New Guinea, Somalia, Niger). This year (2018) appears to be a more challenged year with respect to total numbers of WPV1 associated cases and ever-increasing numbers of cVDPV cases.

